messages.message:
just fyi, if anyone is seeing Travis errors unrelated to your code in the morning, please pull/rebase on top of latest master. https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/11282 should fix it. Error will look like:
```
$ if [ "$TRAVIS_PULL_REQUEST" != "false" ]; then cd ${TRAVIS_BUILD_DIR}/tools/releasetools/travis && make -s test-changes-in-docker; fi
docker: invalid reference format.
See 'docker run --help'.
make: *** [test-changes-in-docker] Error 125
The command "if [ "$TRAVIS_PULL_REQUEST" != "false" ]; then cd ${TRAVIS_BUILD_DIR}/tools/releasetools/travis && make -s test-changes-in-docker; fi" exited with 2.
```
